      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BANDIT DARYL (1) finds it hard to break through. Better run when finding the frame last time though, finishing second (34.79) at this track. Solid record at the distance winning four races. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Makes plenty of appeal. PRISON BREAK (6) rises 85m in distance at his first try over the longer trip. Scored last start (29.59) over 515m at Sandown. With even luck and a clean start can sneak into the finish. INFRA ROCK (8) stuck on well last time to finish a neck back in second (34.37) at Sandown in a Grade 4/5 over 595m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Winning chance. LIGHTNING QUICK (2) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.",
